      <section class="about-me">
        <h1>Brock Maraee Rohloff â€” Web Developer</h1>
        <div>
          <p>For most of my life, I have consistently let myself down. I wasn't living up to my expectations of
            myself. But I wanted to change and I sought an opportunity to do it.
          </p>
          <p>That opportunity was a career change following acceptance to Lambda School. I saved
            for months so that I could quit my job and give my new career everything that I had. Now I'm
            ready to enter the workforce, addicted to the satisfaction that comes from digging through a
            problem and unearthing a solution.
          </p>
          <p>I finally feel like I'm living up to my expectations of myself, and I can't wait to take the next
            step further, and give back to an industry that is making this possible.
          </p>
        </div>
